Preheat oven to 350 degrees F. Wash apples and core using an apple corer. Place in a 9X13-inch baking pan. Mix together SPLENDA(R) Granulated Sweetener and cinnamon. Fill each apple with the mixture and then top each apple with a small dot of margarine. Cover with aluminum foil and bake in preheated oven 45 to 50 minutes or until slightly soft.